title: GIRL TALK: periods, UTIs, sex

description:
Brooke and Danielle are getting into some topics that were highly requested in today’s GIRL TALK episode.  The gals get into their period stories, UTI treatment/advice, routines for when things may get a little ~spicy~, and intimacy.  Also, join the gals as they catch up on their crazy weekend adventures with visiting Athens and attending a wedding!  Be sure to tag @galsonthegopodcast in your listening selfies/stories on Instagram!
